    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109010/extras/28cd85a3d6036cf01aa6320806bea82d.poster.avif?t=1750330793\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109010/extras/28cd85a3d6036cf01aa6320806bea82d.webm?t=1750330793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109010/extras/28cd85a3d6036cf01aa6320806bea82d.mp4?t=1750330793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>THE GIST</strong></i></u><strong></strong><br>YOYO PUNK is a Rope-Physics battleground. You play as a tough rebellious <strong>yoyo</strong>, swinging, flailing and crushing other yoyo opponents in intense, fast action, PVP combat arenas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>SMOOTH LIKE BUTTER</strong></i></u><br>After a long time of development, we're extremly proud of YOYO PUNK's intuitive grappling. try it for yourself!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>EASY TO WIN - HARD TO MASTER</strong></i></u><strong></strong><br>The large variety of traverse options allow you to optimize your locomotion, come at your opponnent as fast as you possibly can to deliver powerful and accurate momentum-based attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109010/extras/511f59fa34e454cab3c8db534f2ced23.avif?t=1750330793\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109010/extras_big/511f59fa34e454cab3c8db534f2ced23.avif?t=1750330793 width=800 height=422 /></span></p></li></ul>",
